Show option values:confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a "Controllers" -g
Display option help:confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a "Controllers" -d
Change option values:confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a "Controllers" -s
Change all option values:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a "Controllers" | more
Reset all option values:confopts_ph.sh -p reset -a "Controllers" | more
List all options:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a "Controllers" | more
Go to Controllers:ph_show_menu Controllers
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
Open a shell (Type CTRL-D to return):cd;/bin/bash
Quit:break
Return to previous screen:return
